name: E. D. Lundy, Appellant, v. Hettie Hunter Lundy, Appellee

judges: Whitfield, P. J., and Strum and Buford, J. J., concur.
.Terrell, C. J., and Ellis and Brown, J. J., concur in the opinion and judgment.
parties: E. D. Lundy, Appellant, v. Hettie Hunter Lundy, Appellee.

opinions.text:
Per Curiam.
The decree herein dismissing on the evidence a bill of complaint seeking the dissolution of the marriage relation on the ground of fraud upon the husband, a minor, who was unaware of his spouse’s condition at the marriage, is reversed.
Whitfield, P. J., and Strum and Buford, J. J., concur.
.Terrell, C. J., and Ellis and Brown, J. J., concur in the opinion and judgment.
opinions.author: Per Curiam.
